message.body: Bonnie once told me about a Boeing ski club logo that looks like a Chinnook skiing. Do you have any idea where I could find this picture?
I can't find it on either shitty website. Maybe one of the officers has it.
Can you see if you can get it from them for me and email it to me? I'm
working on a surprise for Bonnie I think she would like it but I need that picture
